title: Valar Rereadis: TWOIAF - The Stepstones
description:
Perhaps the busiest shipping region in the world, also an anarchic haunt of pirates and slavers. Westeros will suffer greatly if the wrong people take over the islands... Featuring: Princes Daemon, Aemon and Baelon, Oakenfist, Racallio Ryndoon, the Golden Company, Maelys Blackfyre and the Band of Nine, the Kingdom of the Three Daughters, Asha, the Red Kraken, Salladhor Saan, his ancestors and many more.
